name: HAIR EXTENSIONS SERVICE PERTH GIRLS
description:
WANT LONG, SEXY HAIR FOR SUMMER?

HAIR EXTENSIONS SERVICE 

For PERTH girls
 

You will receive: 

200 Strands Pre Bonded I-tip 22" long 100% Human Remy Hair - this is a lot of hair! you will more than likely have spare hair left over. Human Hair means you can curl, straighten, blow wave, everything you would do to your real hair normally.

Microlink method of application - minimal damage to your real hair, unlike glue ins and other methods.

Fast application - 2-3 hours max  which I provide from the comfort of my home studio.

THERE IS NO BETTER FEELING THAN LONG SEXY HAIR - having great, eye-catching hair will give you more fun and excitement in your life! Hair can be re-used over and over again. You just have to look after it, which is very simple to do, and the hair can last you many applications. All that needs to be re-bought are the beads, which are very cheap (approx $35).

You will get a Care Instructions print out at the consultation. 

FREE CONSULTATION INCLUSIVE- perfect colour match Application done in the privacy of my studio at home. Extensions last for 6-8 weeks before they need shifting up. I also provide this service for just $35 per hour and that generally takes 2-3 hours. 

 

NOW THE STEPS YOU NEED TO TAKE: 

1. Msg me to arrange a consultation date. If you have a special occasion, please allow 2 weeks before the date of this occasion to have your consult. We will work out the day and time, and I will forward you my address. After hours and weekend times are available.

2. Consultation : here we will match up your real hair, and discuss anything further you would like to know.

3. We will then arrange a time and date for your application in the next 7-10 days.

4. Application - takes approx 3 hours max.  Movies and light refreshments provided. 

5. You may want to get your hair extensions cut to your desired length, as well as layered into, at your hairdressers afterwards. 

 

PLEASE DON’T HESITATE TO CONTACT ME - send me ur email address and I can send you a more detailed info pack on my Hair Extension Service I provide - especially to take up this fabulous offer I have going! Times and dates can become very limited.

name: CLIP IN EXTENSIONS 20" long
description:
10 PC CLIP IN SET
20" LONG
100% REMY HUMAN HAIR
80 GRAM

The perfect alternative to permanent extensions, clip in extensions are best for weekends and special occassions.

If local in Perth, I am able to show you how to put them in.

It is best to meet with me for a colour match up.

If not local to Perth, they can be dyed to suit if need be.

please allow 3-5 working days to receive your order.
